  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      this research will evaluate the effect of PRF with different bioactive materials in dentistry
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      PRF will be used with MTA and Theracal to evaluate its effect upon these materials in
      reliving pain and maintains the teeth vitality in permanent teeth with closed apices, in
      order to improve the materials outcome.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
